Greece and Ellinikí Radiofonía Tileórasi (ERT) chose to host a National Selection with the winner being chosen by  SMS voting (30%), televoting (30%) and an "expert" jury (40%).
Mando was chosen with "Never Let You Go" and achieved 17th place in Eurovision.
The hosts of the show were Dafni Bokota, Rika Vagiani &amp; Popi Tsapanidou.
